b'Duel Masters Cross':
b'Shobu and friends fight the remaining Fua Duelists in order to defeat Zakira. Once again, they face off against the old members of Fua Duelists at the World Championship tournament.

Shobu also found the terrible fate his friends faced because of these duelists in their past.
